prompt.title: Embedding for Promptbook: Ecosystem for AI Applications
prompt.content: The Promptbook ecosystem includes the Book language, Promptbook Engine (for running Book applications), and Promptbook Studio (a web-based editor and runner for Book applications). It also has a community of developers and users, as well as branded social media presence.
